      • getReportDownloadTimeout

        @Nullable
public Integer getReportDownloadTimeout()
        Return the non-negative download timeout in milliseconds. A value of 0 (zero) indicates infinite timeout. A value of null indicates that the default timeout from AdWordsLibConfiguration.getReportDownloadTimeout() should be used.
        Returns:
        the timeout in milliseconds, or null if no timeout was specified.
